{"tid":1891413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對所有醫護最後一次警告","createTime":"2020-02-21T21:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T01:15:28.000Z","uid":112581,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f02d4da6ee667c2d3d74d8bd4cfa70076ba569","tid":1891413,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T21:39:29.000Z","msg":"假如任何一個醫護因為罷工比人炒<br />\n所有工會成員一定要立即辭職<br />\n唔好同我講咩等法律程序解決<br />\n仲相信香港有法治既人本身就抵死<br />\n就算好彩比你JR到中間已經出現好撚多個受害者<br />\n同一招對付得你一個工會自然可以拎黎對付其他工會<br />\n希望下面幅圖日後唔洗拎黎串醫護手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/07/wFK4H0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2FwFK4H0.png&h=34f10f7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b15d5bb5719f80be6c2a820a7ab50716c3803e63","tid":1891413,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T21:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />agger"},{"pid":"60aab6e4dd78cf7fb4bd91c0100ac861fcfa9295","tid":1891413,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T21:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5daf76c15feacb7b3fadfff1f44829d145a9c94","tid":1891413,"uid":260195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T21:50:59.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"f406948874d6bbffd1dc9a9309c44d7f4c7c140a","tid":1891413,"uid":205566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T21:52:19.000Z","msg":"咁樣的確係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972a603c8147eba00fd7bacc0cc6b12060d2e348","tid":1891413,"uid":237222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T21:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個狀況可以去到任何一個行業  佢地一定會想囉你地黎試水溫<br />\n<br />\n團結一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我認為其他工會都要著手去準備"},{"pid":"a9a9b0bef19a349ccb79bce408b24cda8946a869","tid":1891413,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T22:04:39.000Z","msg":"嘩 巧威威wo 又教人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda5bb404dda91fa2d94f0478c97408324a2bd19","tid":1891413,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T22:05:32.000Z","msg":"發動工業行動係唔需要辭職的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb7c0723d85e5fd40b81b509f2df656e64aee7b","tid":1891413,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T22:08:21.000Z","msg":"同意，但一定做唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b691e6f25badd798ff7a6d94b7e22393afda79fc","tid":1891413,"uid":15916,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T22:09:06.000Z","msg":"警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你落場做搞手叫人辭職啦 講經<br />\n串手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化不割席講左幾耐 你串啲咩"},{"pid":"aafd1563b789335f5443f25fcbd006c1baf8030a","tid":1891413,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9a9b0bef19a349ccb79bce408b24cda8946a869","tid":1891413,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T22:04:39.000Z","msg":"嘩 巧威威wo 又教人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T22:09:39.000Z","msg":"都未夠200萬條港豬教年年考第一既淋病做野咁威啦柒頭"},{"pid":"47b31cf5bda2c516b1d2083a4a22848afaef46e6","tid":1891413,"uid":112581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b691e6f25badd798ff7a6d94b7e22393afda79fc","tid":1891413,"uid":15916,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T22:09:06.000Z","msg":"警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你落場做搞手叫人辭職啦 講經<br />\n串手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化不割席講左幾耐 你串啲咩"},"